quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 16px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: normal;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;font-weight: bolder;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24897959183673468\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"980\" style=\"width: 106px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/cNFA8C0uVPuQzlZAjS66ZEYbDkdc0DAaC7AvbxPrUmFpdQ5eozPic4tSVCN0YvwfgRX5AIqSHKx8mic2s2a0DjoQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"106\" data-cropsely2=\"22\" data-imgfileid=\"100241827\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=404aa831&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FcNFA8C0uVPuQzlZAjS66ZEYbDkdc0DAaC7AvbxPrUmFpdQ5eozPic4tSVCN0YvwfgRX5AIqSHKx8mic2s2a0DjoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></span></strong></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">提起来Agent，最先被关注的肯定是被 Meta 收购的 Manus，而在硅谷投资圈内，另一家 Agent 公司 Genspark 同样备受关注，不仅得到了硅谷主流基金的青睐，有传闻称，Genspark 也同样进入到了硅谷大厂的视野范围之内。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Genspark 与 Manus 同为华人创办，都是 AI Agent赛道的顶流公司，有着类似的产品定位和营销打法，他们也是中国最新一代全球化AI创业公司的集中缩影。大众对于Manus的故事耳熟能详，我们也即将发布《我所认识的肖弘》一文，关于Genspark的背景经历，相比较而言知之者要少得多。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknyndm71nwi\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mba8mvlk1t2b\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;padding: 0px 14px 0px 14px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"width: 38px;height: 38px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin-bottom: -38px;margin-left: -20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1.0075757575757576\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"132\" style=\"display: block;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 38px !important;background-color: transparent;\" data-imgfileid=\"100241584\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dbc1c31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FcNFA8C0uVPsftdZPOcWcnkWugp5Shs2EFib7ZU93GBp4DqVXhrOBCQKQzxcyAIzj1mUKiawHRm6xD4obGgROJm7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1\"></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"font-size:36px;line-height:50px;\" data-mid=\"\"><strong mpa-none-content=\"t\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n          <br> \n         </span><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">硅谷原生的华人明星创企</span></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">2024年6月，由百度集团前副总裁景鲲（Eric Jing）创立的MainFunc推出首款产品Genspark，主攻的方向就是硅谷炙手可热的赛道“AI搜索”，彼时，AI搜索领域的明星公司 Perplexity 估值已经达到30亿美元，并正在计划新的一轮2.5亿C轮融资，此时Genspark迅速切入该赛道。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">创始人景鲲曾任小度科技CEO，代表作品是小度音箱，加入百度前，是微软首席研发总监，负责微软必应搜索亚洲市场的研发工作，也是微软小冰的创造者之一。Genspark联合创始人朱凯华曾任谷歌主任架构师、百度集团智能助手首席架构师、小度CTO， Genspark 作为明星团队创业，加上敏锐的商业嗅觉，在这个阶段，也迅速在AI搜索领域站稳脚跟，拿到新加坡蓝驰创投投资的种子轮6000万美元，估值来到了2.6亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">而与此同时，Manus 的母公司蝴蝶效应，创立已经一年半，经历了两轮融资，估值却只有6000万美元。和景鲲比起来，肖弘的背景简直属于草根创业：无大厂经历，无明星产品，无资本背景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">更明显的区别是，景鲲创立的MainFunc是一家扎根于硅谷的国际化团队，肖弘创立的蝴蝶效应，是一家武汉原生的中国团队。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">MainFunc 的融资节奏快得惊人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">MainFunc 的种子轮，于2024年中完成，估值约6000万美元，彼时MainFunc的核心业务，还只是在做AI 搜索。一年后，2025年2月MainFunc完成1亿美元A轮融资，估值跃升至5.3亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">对比来看，2024年11月，蝴蝶效应拿到红杉资本领投的B轮融资时，估值还不到1亿美金。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknyo6t51a3h\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mba8mvlk1t2b\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;padding: 0px 14px 0px 14px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"width: 38px;height: 38px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin-bottom: -38px;margin-left: -20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1.0075757575757576\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"132\" style=\"display: block;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 38px !important;background-color: transparent;\" data-imgfileid=\"100241584\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dbc1c31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FcNFA8C0uVPsftdZPOcWcnkWugp5Shs2EFib7ZU93GBp4DqVXhrOBCQKQzxcyAIzj1mUKiawHRm6xD4obGgROJm7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1\"></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"font-size:36px;line-height:50px;\" data-mid=\"\"><strong mpa-none-content=\"t\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n          <br> \n         </span><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">探寻与摸索：从AI搜索到Agent</span></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">至此，一家是AI搜索公司，一家是浏览器插件公司，虽然都是Chatbot类型产品，但资本故事截然不同，大概率也是碰不到彼此的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">转折点在于2025 年3月6日，Manus Agent正式发布，不仅创造了通用型Agent的新赛道，而且立刻成为了一个现象级事件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">AI的价值不在于简单的聊天和互动，不在于内容的生成，更在于推理、决策和执行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">这个共识性认知一瞬间席卷全球，Agent才是未来，AI搜索早已是明日黄花。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">事实也的确如此。Perplexity很快就被市场遗忘，Genspark已经在准备调整方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">距离Manus发布不到一个月的时间，4月2日Genspark的核心产品Super Agent上线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">进入Agent赛道之后，Genspark从人气表现上一直略逊于Manus。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Manus一上市月活就迅速突破2000万，国内市场邀请码一码难求，之后又迅速在硅谷爆红，特别是在 Discord社区。据AI科技评论了解，当时面对突如其来的访问量，蝴蝶效应公司一度接近宕机，创始人肖弘带着团队维护服务器，抢救流量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">据 Similarweb统计，Manus 在 2025 年 3 月的月访问量达到了2376 万人次。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"317\" data-backw=\"546\" data-height=\"606\" data-imgfileid=\"100247152\" data-ratio=\"0.5804597701149425\" style=\"background-color:transparent;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1044\" data-width=\"1044\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e9107e18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FcNFA8C0uVPsiapczKvP7znMBTwombRdDRP3l7vKKgrsxwamlm1b2m478ia5eM6icVmIpcjD4P1EX3YTNDfvNLsLFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Manus发布一个月后，蝴蝶效应拿到了Benchmark的融资，估值来到5亿美元。这也是中国本土的AI创业公司第一次拿到美国主流美元基金的投资。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">但是两家公司最根本的差异很快显现出来。2025年6月，蝴蝶效应选择了裁撤中国员工、清空中国社媒，这些行为，被市场解读为这家公司已经全面搬迁至海外。而Genspark完全没有这种忧虑。这是一家原生的全球化公司，包括市场从一开始是全球化的，融资是全球化的，增长、产品、运营都是全球化的，甚至招人上，Genspark也是全球化的，这是一条押注全球的路线。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">2025年11月，通过B轮融资，Genspark估值已经达到了12.5亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">在全球化的AI时代，做“原生的全球化公司”，不论在资本市场还是在全球人才吸纳上，都会更具竞争力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">据AI科技评论了解，已经完成3000 万美元融资的Fellou AI 浏览器，去年六月份之后，也在寻求搬迁至海外。此外，还有激光雷达上市公司禾赛科技三位创始人向少卿、李一帆、孙恺共同创立的灵巧手公司 Sharpa ，也直接选择在新加坡架设公司，直接搭建原生全球化公司的框架。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknyp0vob7h\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mba8mvlk1t2b\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;padding: 0px 14px 0px 14px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"width: 38px;height: 38px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin-bottom: -38px;margin-left: -20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1.0075757575757576\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"132\" style=\"display: block;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 38px !important;background-color: transparent;\" data-imgfileid=\"100241584\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dbc1c31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FcNFA8C0uVPsftdZPOcWcnkWugp5Shs2EFib7ZU93GBp4DqVXhrOBCQKQzxcyAIzj1mUKiawHRm6xD4obGgROJm7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1\"></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"font-size:36px;line-height:50px;\" data-mid=\"\"><strong mpa-none-content=\"t\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n          <br> \n         </span><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Agent的较量之路</span></span></strong></strong></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">为什么在Manus 已经成为行业现象级产品的情况下，Genspark还能够突出重围，持续融资，在多位硅谷科技人士看来，他们做对了以下几件事：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">第一是在营销模式上，Genspark学会了</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">制造话题与传播事件</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">，引起AI大网红的共谋式传播，而非追求投流转化率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">肖弘的Manus和景鲲的Genspark都心照不宣，采用了这样的模式。如果你注意Genspark的社媒，会发现它现在还在坚持每周发布一项“the first in the world.....”级别的声明。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">某种程度上，AI 技术仍处在快速进化期：模型能力、交互范式与应用形态都在高频迭代，用户对“确定性产出”的预期尚未稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">在这种背景下，C 端的核心诉求往往不只是把某个任务更高效地做完（比如一键生成 PPT、写周报），而是亲身感受前沿能力带来的“新鲜感”和“可能性”——看它能否理解更复杂的意图、能否更自然地对话、能否在多模态中完成更像人的表达。由此，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">产品竞争也更像技术秀场：谁更快把新能力包装成可感知的体验，谁就更容易获得注意力与口碑。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">第二是</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">在产品迭代速度上，Genspark也做出了特色。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">一位同样在硅谷做Agent创业的从业人员跟AI科技评论提过一个数据，Genspark 能在一个MAU（月活用户）身上赚大约 8 毛，Manus 能赚一块5，但从退订率的角度，某Genspark投资人表示，Genspark的退订率只有Manus 的1/ 3。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Genspark的用户留存策略，在于它的 tool box 的定位和产品迭代速度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">从产品层面，根据多位资深用户的体验，Genspark 有两个特点，第一是聚焦，Genspark 聚焦在办公自动化、数据分析和文件管理，这些都是企业的刚需场景，用户往往是企业，有着非常高的付费意愿。第二是自我迭代， Genspark 的Super Agent 从上线以来，几乎保持每周一次的更新节奏，无论是AI Slides 2.0，还是多智能体调度系统，以及早期推出的AI Sheets、AI Docs，都深受大家喜欢。并且每月甚至每周都会推出新产品和工具，虽品类分散，但用户会因不断有新东西且价格不贵而愿意持续不断给Genspark续费，这才让它做到了很低的退订率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">这样在国内积累的产品思维和效率，到了海外市场，几乎是降维打击，也让Genspark的付费用户留存率维持非常高的水准，达到了88%-92%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">第三点则是团队构成。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">这样的营销模式和产品迭代，跟Genspark的团队构成有着分不开的关系。Genspark的成员，既有来自国内字节百度等互联网大厂，也有来自硅谷AI领域的从业者，但整体来看，Genspark招人非常精准的，是能快速融入团队，整个团队是以中国人为首的global team。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">这种配置让Genspark能够实现“中国的工程密度”与“硅谷产品节奏”，他们既能在短周期内实现复杂功能上线，也能迅速对接国际投资人与媒体叙事。</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mknypndq912\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mba8mvlk1t2b\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;padding: 0px 14px 0px 14px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"display: flex;justify-content: flex-start;align-items: center;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"width: 38px;height: 38px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin-bottom: -38px;margin-left: -20px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"1.0075757575757576\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"132\" style=\"display: block;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 38px !important;background-color: transparent;\" data-imgfileid=\"100241584\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6dbc1c31&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FcNFA8C0uVPsftdZPOcWcnkWugp5Shs2EFib7ZU93GBp4DqVXhrOBCQKQzxcyAIzj1mUKiawHRm6xD4obGgROJm7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1\"></p>\n      <div style=\"text-align: center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"font-size:36px;line-height:50px;\" data-mid=\"\"><strong mpa-none-content=\"t\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n          <br> \n         </span><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h2&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">一家Agent公司的终局：</span></span></strong></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"font-size:36px;line-height:50px;\" data-mid=\"\"><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">独立还是被收购</span></span></strong><strong style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"flex-direction:column;font-weight:bold;font-size:18px;justify-content:flex-start;line-height:25px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;align-items:center;text-align:center;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">？</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">在Manus被收购之后，有传闻称Genspark也在同硅谷大厂接触。对于Agent公司为什么被大厂收购，有业内人士给过我们这样的复盘：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">在2025年以前，所有人都曾认为，大模型是新时代OS级别的大机会。但在Agent出现之后，这一认知逐渐被打破。未来的“操作系统”需要管理的是AI模型的能力、多样的工具和复杂的任务，Agent才是能够成为连接所有工具完成任务，并且与用户直接交互的操作系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">从PC时代到移动互联网时代，移动操作系统一直是典型的“大厂的游戏”，需要庞大的资本、顶级的硬件整合能力和一个繁荣的开发者生态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">这一观点可能会在一些垂直市场被打破，但在通用级别的市场，一个闭源的Agent，想要在激烈的竞争中脱颖而出，所需要的海量的资源，远远不是一家创业公司所能承受的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">在目前的Agent缺乏上游的基模壁垒的情况下，只能依靠下游的产品形态和用户体验来打造壁垒。在当前的代际，纯Agent应用层的独立性是非常脆弱的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 16px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">真正的竞争还未开始。而这场竞争一旦开始，那就是Google、Microsoft、字节与腾讯等顶级大厂之间的比赛，Agent最后的赢家一定属于最清醒的玩家。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度剖析了 AI Agent 明星创企 Genspark 如何凭借原生全球化架构、高频产品迭代及差异化营销，在激烈竞争中脱颖而出并获得资本青睐。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度剖析了 AI Agent 明星创企 Genspark 如何凭借原生全球化架构、高频产品迭代及差异化营销，在激烈竞争中脱颖而出并获得资本青睐。",
  "summary": "文章详细对比了 Genspark 与 Manus 两家由华人创立的顶尖 AI Agent 公司。Genspark 由百度前副总裁景鲲创立，凭借其“原生全球化”的团队背景，在融资节奏、人才吸纳和资本市场对接上展现出显著优势。文章指出，Genspark 的成功在于：一是采用“技术秀场”式的营销模式，通过制造话题维持品牌热度；二是保持极高的产品迭代频率，聚焦办公自动化等刚需场景，实现了远高于行业平均水平的用户留存率；三是融合了“中国工程密度”与“硅谷产品节奏”的团队配置。最后，文章探讨了 Agent 公司的终局，认为在缺乏上游基模壁垒的情况下，纯应用层 Agent 最终可能走向被科技巨头收购的命运。",
  "mainPoints": [
